topic.title: Namecoin users on Zeronet
topic.body:
Hi there,

Anybody actively using nmc feel free to say hello.
topic.body_p: Hi there,Anybody actively using nmc feel free to say hello.

comment.body: The issue is technical ability, motivation and time. I would say motivation is probably the most important but also if you are not technically able Windows seems (unfortunately) ideal. Thanks for spreading the word though! F(L)OSS hopefully can only grow with movements such as cryptocurrency because the flaws of proprietary software can strike a chord with people when it comes to their savings :)
